 \subsection{RMSE}
 
 $RMSE$ measures the average difference between a the hindcast and the observation.
 
$$RMSE=\sqrt{\frac{1}{n} \sum\limits_{i=1}^{n}(H_i -O_i)^2}$$
where :
\begin{itemize}
	\item H : the Hindcast.
	\item O : the observation.
	\item i : the valid time.
\end{itemize}